Overview

This is a simple web project for displaying doctor-related content. 
It includes an HTML page, CSS styling, and a backend server using Node.js.

Project Structure

├── public/               
│   ├── doctors.jpeg
│   ├── health.jpeg
│   ├── patient.jpeg
│   ├── pdashboard.jpeg
│   └── doctor.jpeg
├── css/
│   └── doctor.css       
├── html/
│   ├── doctor.html
│   ├── book-appointment.html
│   ├── login.html
│   ├── signup.html
│   ├── profile.html
│   └── patient_dashboard.html
├── .gitattributes
├── .gitignore
└── server.js 

Technologies Used

HTML5
CSS3
Node.js
SQL
